FIGURES 14‒21.

Xysticus spasskyi

, specimens from the Crimea. 14‒15, 17‒18 Male palp (14 ventral, 15 retrolateral, 17 anterior, 18 ventro-prolateral); 16 tip of embolus and tutaculum, ventral; 19‒21 Epigyne (19 after maceration, dorsal, 20 after maceration, ventral; 21 anterior-ventral). Scale = 0.1 mm. Abbreviations: 
